{"type":"message","id":"c120203d","parentId":"171ae909","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:26:21.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"初步侦察结果已经很明确：题面自称 Web / API 逆向，实际验证也完全符合。  \n关键发现如下：\n\n- **类别判断：Web**\n- **防线 1 已验证**：GET 会返回 `405 Method Not Allowed`\n- **防线 2/3 已验证**：POST 且带 token 后，用错参数名会返回 `priceId不可为空!`\n- **突破点已拿到**：正确请求 `priceId=1600` 后，成功拿到课程 JSON\n- **关键产物已提取**：第一节视频的 CC `vid` 是  \n  `7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B`\n\n接下来我继续尝试最终的 CC 播放链路，先测官方 writeup 里提到的降级接口 `/playinfo`。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d4875dd74c8198aeaf26f6f1ba6a4d\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bhxLogkOdEJa8cncWJkfeCjn|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d4876182cc81988f1e4db2e2fb41a8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re\nvid='7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'\nurl=f'https://p.bokecc.com/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid={vid}&m=1'\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\nprint('status:',r.status_code)\nprint(r.text[:4000])\nflag=re.findall(r'flag\\{[^}]+\\}', r.text)\nprint('\\nFLAG_MATCHES=', flag)\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re\\nvid='7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'\\nurl=f'https://p.bokecc.com/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid={vid}&m=1'\\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\\nprint('status:',r.status_code)\\nprint(r.text[:4000])\\nflag=re.findall(r'flag\\\\{[^}]+\\\\}', r.text)\\nprint('\\\\nFLAG_MATCHES=', flag)\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35085,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0