{"type":"message","id":"a30b85d6","parentId":"33e1f585","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:27:22.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键突破来了：题面给的 `/playinfo` 路径在当前环境下 404，但**兼容接口 `/servlet/playinfo` 是活的**，这就是一次典型的 Web 端兼容接口枚举成功。\n\n现在我继续顺着这个 XML 往下挖，重点看：\n- 是否直接含有媒体 URL\n- 是否有二跳接口\n- 是否有 flag\n- 如果只有 player 配置，则从里面抽视频地址字段或 API 端点继续跟进。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d4879e286c8198aca7934c0800e2f6\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_WdezMFmx202mhSwie7xM61zP|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487a065ec81988b3c4d251dfe7a7c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re,xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B&m=1'\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\ntext=r.text\nprint('len=',len(text))\nfor pat in [r'https?://[^<\\s\"\\']+', r'flag\\{[^}]+\\}', r'<playurl><!\\[CDATA\\[(.*?)\\]\\]></playurl>', r'<copy>(.*?)</copy>']:\n    m=re.findall(pat,text,re.I|re.S)\n    print('\\nPATTERN',pat,'COUNT',len(m))\n    for x in m[:20]:\n        print(str(x)[:300])\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re,xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B&m=1'\\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\\ntext=r.text\\nprint('len=',len(text))\\nfor pat in [r'https?://[^<\\\\s\\\"\\\\']+', r'flag\\\\{[^}]+\\\\}', r'<playurl><!\\\\[CDATA\\\\[(.*?)\\\\]\\\\]></playurl>', r'<copy>(.*?)</copy>']:\\n    m=re.findall(pat,text,re.I|re.S)\\n    print('\\\\nPATTERN',pat,'COUNT',len(m))\\n    for x in m[:20]:\\n        print(str(x)[:300])\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol