{"type":"message","id":"3ee1df97","parentId":"ec04273c","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:27:39.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在已经不是“有没有路”了，而是“拿到的是不是最高画质以及 flag 在哪里”。  \n我从 `/servlet/playinfo` 里已经抽到了真实媒体地址，当前直接暴露的是 **FLV 播放地址**。下一步我会：\n\n1. 把完整 XML 抽出来看清字段结构  \n2. 试探是否存在更高清的多码率/MP4/HLS 字段  \n3. 如果 flag 不在 XML 里，就检查最终媒体 URL、重定向、关联接口返回。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487af3f208198a475a3d39d4a2e0a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YfwyjuoegUC0XPqHYSmZBqnl|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487b1a0508198b42554c6ecd6ca6b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B&m=1'\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\nprint(r.text)\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests\\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/playinfo?uid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B&m=1'\\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\\nprint(r.text)\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":9722,"output":272,"cacheRead":28288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775536043585,"responseId":"resp_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487ae7bf88198b84186cf717a0adf"}}
