{"type":"message","id":"589df2d6","parentId":"e6771b57","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:28:06.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这里已经拿到结构化证据了：\n\n- `<quality value=\"9\" desp=\"原画\">`  \n  说明当前返回的就是**最高画质：原画**\n- 对应直链是：\n  - `http://cp15-c120-1.play.bokecc.com/flvs/ca/QxgvX/6NfU5d75Qk-9.flv?...`\n  - 以及一个备份域名 `cp12-...`\n\n但这条真实链路里**没有 flag 参数**。  \n这说明两种可能：\n\n1. 题目文本自带的是“官方 writeup 示例”，flag 已写死在题面里  \n2. 真实服务还有别的返回分支（比如 MP4/HLS/JSON）里带 flag，需要继续枚举\n\n我继续围绕已拿到的 `verifystr / cid / quality / playurl / player JS` 做 Web 侧侦察，看看能不能把 mp4/m3u8 或 flag 再挖出来。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487bf8c94819884af68372b3d8446\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ybRfIOLe2Iby5sw9EZZqrWeR|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487c3cadc819882a2e573da82e5fa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re\njs=requests.get('https://p.bokecc.com/js/player/v20200701.js',timeout=20).text\nprint('len',len(js))\nfor pat in ['m3u8','mp4','playurl','quality','servlet/playinfo','api/video','verifystr','flag{']:\n    print('\\n---',pat,'---')\n    idx=js.find(pat)\n    print('idx',idx)\n    if idx!=-1:\n        print(js[max(0,idx-300):idx+700])\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re\\njs=requests.get('https://p.bokecc.com/js/player/v20200701.js',timeout=20).text\\nprint('len',len(js))\\nfor pat in ['m3u8','mp4','playurl','quality','servlet/playinfo','api/video','verifystr','flag{']:\\n    print('\\\\n---',pat,'---')\\n    idx=js.find(pat)\\n    print('idx',idx)\\n    if idx!=-1:\\n        print(js[max(0,idx-300):idx+700])\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":39498,"output":400,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cache