{"type":"message","id":"24dffad1","parentId":"e527d2a3","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:28:32.099Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"JS 里能看出播放器支持多种介质，但我们当前 XML 只返回了一个 quality=9 的 FLV copy。为了尽可能把题做实，我再做两件事：\n\n1. 直接请求这条 FLV，看是否 302 到带 flag 的最终地址  \n2. 枚举与播放信息相关的常见 CC 接口/参数，看看有没有返回 JSON/MP4/M3U8 的兼容端点\n\n这一步仍然属于 Web/API 侦察，不需要切去 reverse。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487db5d708198a6acc20b671ffa20\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Coegaops0CfdbrgcF0MkbrAB|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487ddb2208198add284f5c29f51bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re,html\nplay='http://cp15-c120-1.play.bokecc.com/flvs/ca/QxgvX/6NfU5d75Qk-9.flv?t=1775543260&key=5CEEF5D5188864FF5971783FEA08C3DC&tpl=10&tpt=111'\ntry:\n    r=requests.get(play,timeout=20,allow_redirects=False,stream=True)\n    print('status',r.status_code)\n    print('headers',dict(r.headers))\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('ERR',repr(e))\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re,html\\nplay='http://cp15-c120-1.play.bokecc.com/flvs/ca/QxgvX/6NfU5d75Qk-9.flv?t=1775543260&key=5CEEF5D5188864FF5971783FEA08C3DC&tpl=10&tpt=111'\\ntry:\\n    r=requests.get(play,timeout=20,allow_redirects=False,stream=True)\\n    print('status',r.status_code)\\n    print('headers',dict(r.headers))\\nexcept Exception as e:\\n    print('ERR',repr(e))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":41524,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775536086997,"responseId":"resp_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487d9de908198aec38dd9c926d33b"}}
