{"type":"message","id":"09a6596d","parentId":"a1ecdc29","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:29:28.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"结果说明这条 FLV 就是可直接访问的媒体对象，不是 302 包装链，而且 URL 参数里也没有 flag。  \n因此，基于真实探测，目前最可靠的结论是：\n\n- 题目主类：**web**\n- 子方向：**API 逆向 / 接口降级 / 兼容播放接口枚举**\n- 真实服务成功拿到的“最高画质直链”是 **原画 FLV**\n- 但**真实接口响应中未发现 flag**\n- 题面里给出的 “官方 WriteUp” 已经把 flag 示例写出来了\n\n我再做最后一轮小范围枚举，确认是否存在 mp4/m3u8 或其它带 flag 的兼容返回。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487f3f704819889b346732962c128\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_DjG9eRfQ4kMTX76YlJZNZX56|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d487f7243c81988a2ae20735d4a21b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re\nbase='https://p.bokecc.com'\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\npaths=[\n '/servlet/playinfo',\n '/playinfo',\n '/servlet/getvideofile',\n '/api/playurl',\n '/api/playinfo',\n '/api/video/playurl',\n '/api/video/playinfo',\n '/player',\n '/player?siteid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B',\n]\nparam_sets=[\n {'uid':'D00F0DB59DF3AD97','vid':'7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B','m':'1'},\n {'siteid':'D00F0DB59DF3AD97','vid':'7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'},\n {'userid':'D00F0DB59DF3AD97','videoid':'7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'},\n]\nfor p in paths:\n    for params in param_sets:\n        try:\n            r=requests.get(base+p,params=params,headers=headers,timeout=12)\n            text=r.text[:800]\n            if r.status_code!=404 and ('7CDB1897' in r.text or 'm3u8' in r.text or 'mp4' in r.text or 'playurl' in r.text or 'result' in r.text):\n                print('\\n===',r.url,'===')\n                print('status',r.status_code,'ct',r.headers.get('content-type'))\n                print(text.replace('\\n',' ')[:800])\n        except Exception:\n            pass\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"py