{"type":"message","id":"61d15d4e","parentId":"548f6d5b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:29:50.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"又拿到一个更关键的兼容接口：\n\n- `/servlet/getvideofile?siteid=...&vid=...`\n\n这个返回的是 JSONP，而且直接给了 **MP4 原画**：\n- `quality: 90`\n- `desp: 原画`\n- `playurl: http://cm15-c110-1.play.bokecc.com/.../6NfU5d75Qk-90.mp4?...`\n\n这比前面的 FLV 更符合题目“最高清 MP4/M3U8”的要求。  \n我把完整 JSONP 展开一下，确认是否还有更高项、m3u8 项或 flag。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d4883617448198a8837cdca40ed4e5\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_duDbgkWRShTiGenA5OuLwqif|fc_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d48838e49481989dfefd05c115b98f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re,json\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/getvideofile?siteid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\nprint(r.text)\nprint('\\nFLAGS=',re.findall(r'flag\\{[^}]+\\}',r.text))\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re,json\\nurl='https://p.bokecc.com/servlet/getvideofile?siteid=D00F0DB59DF3AD97&vid=7CDB1897C30D1593B463AB73BD4C026B'\\nheaders={'Referer':'http://www.xinghengclass.com/','User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'}\\nr=requests.get(url,headers=headers,timeout=20)\\nprint(r.text)\\nprint('\\\\nFLAGS=',re.findall(r'flag\\\\{[^}]+\\\\}',r.text))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":43747,"output":318,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775536175559,"responseId":"resp_0443c7bf59a5f5f60169d48834a5188198a0cc4d52621d7ce2"}}
