{"type":"message","id":"3bdef0f3","parentId":"b9bae27d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:14:04.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根域名不是前端入口，说明 H5 很可能挂在别的 host/path，或者只开放 API。下一步我从已知接口返回里提取更多页面/资源线索，并对站点做小范围路径侦察，找前端入口与 JS 包。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04268458e98efc8b0169d492923ec8819ba881da8bfa14ba5c\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_HK6XCIul1m1sCWQPvR0etn0x|fc_04268458e98efc8b0169d492939e6c819bbd01e88be40359c3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re,json\nheaders={\n 'token':'71faedd0-3d3c-47bc-a4e7-e4b2576f97ab',\n 'User-Agent':'okhttp/4.9.3',\n 'appTerminal':'iOS',\n 'Content-Type':'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8',\n}\nr=requests.post('https://mobile.xinghengclass.com/timeTable/v5.30.0/getPricesDtail.do',data={'priceId':'1600'},headers=headers,timeout=20)\ntext=r.text\nfor pat in [r'https?://[^\"\\']+', r'[A-Za-z0-9_/.-]+\\.(js|html|htm|apk)', r'bokecc[^\"\\']*', r'xingheng[^\"\\']*']:\n    print('\\nPAT',pat)\n    ms=re.findall(pat,text,re.I)\n    if isinstance(ms,list):\n        uniq=[]\n        for m in ms:\n            s=m if isinstance(m,str) else ''.join(m)\n            if s not in uniq: uniq.append(s)\n        print('\\n'.join(uniq[:50]))\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re,json\\nheaders={\\n 'token':'71faedd0-3d3c-47bc-a4e7-e4b2576f97ab',\\n 'User-Agent':'okhttp/4.9.3',\\n 'appTerminal':'iOS',\\n 'Content-Type':'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8',\\n}\\nr=requests.post('https://mobile.xinghengclass.com/timeTable/v5.30.0/getPricesDtail.do',data={'priceId':'1600'},headers=headers,timeout=20)\\ntext=r.text\\nfor pat in [r'https?://[^\\\"\\\\']+', r'[A-Za-z0-9_/.-]+\\\\.(js|html|htm|apk)', r'bokecc[^\\\"\\\\']*', r'xingheng[^\\\"\\\\']*']:\\n    print('\\\\nPAT',pat)\\n    ms=re.findall(pat,text,re.I)\\n    if isinsta