{"type":"message","id":"17ab442c","parentId":"6791c90a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:15:52.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`/member/shipin.jspx` 更像登录页，首页也只是演示性嵌入播放器，还没看到签名链。为了避免盲扫，我直接在官网 HTML 里抽出所有 `/web/...` AJAX 接口，再针对“video/play/cc”语义做聚焦枚举。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04268458e98efc8b0169d492feee9c819b8f29772eb1802c81\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f7BiBpaYtu6quKkXVorfNesj|fc_04268458e98efc8b0169d4930070e8819bb9b2722dd4b4a39f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport requests,re,urllib.parse\npages=['http://www.xinghengclass.com/','http://www.xinghengclass.com/member/shipin.jspx','http://www.xinghengclass.com/webapp/list?zhuanye=ZHIYEYISHI&type=1','http://www.xinghengclass.com/kcb/']\nall_paths=set()\nfor u in pages:\n    try:\n        t=requests.get(u,headers={'User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'},timeout=20).text\n    except Exception:\n        continue\n    for m in re.findall(r'(/(?:web|member|timeTable|video|play)[^\"\\'\\s<>]+)', t, re.I):\n        all_paths.add(m)\nprint('PATHS',len(all_paths))\nfor p in sorted(all_paths):\n    print(p)\nPY","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport requests,re,urllib.parse\\npages=['http://www.xinghengclass.com/','http://www.xinghengclass.com/member/shipin.jspx','http://www.xinghengclass.com/webapp/list?zhuanye=ZHIYEYISHI&type=1','http://www.xinghengclass.com/kcb/']\\nall_paths=set()\\nfor u in pages:\\n    try:\\n        t=requests.get(u,headers={'User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'},timeout=20).text\\n    except Exception:\\n        continue\\n    for m in re.findall(r'(/(?:web|member|timeTable|video|play)[^\\\"\\\\'\\\\s<>]+)', t, re.I):\\n        all_paths.add(m)\\nprint('PATHS',len(all_paths))\\nfor p in sorted(all_paths):\\n    print(p)\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provide