{"type":"message","id":"d8cdb0ec","parentId":"ea82d25d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:39:23.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，我继续静态挖。  \n我下一步就专门还原这两块：\n\n1. `BaseVodRequest::fillPopRequestInfo` 到底塞了哪些字段  \n2. `PopRequest::getSign` 到底拿哪些输入算签名\n\n等我把“签名入参链”抠出来后，再给你一个更像答案的结论：  \n**哪些参数必须有、哪些是设备/证书相关、哪些是服务端返回不可本地伪造。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_017e4306923e27190169d4a696b83c8198bb89f6ec4077f696\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":44498,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775543950494,"responseId":"resp_017e4306923e27190169d4a694d0108198bfa8fc4e47ac883f"}}
