{"type":"message","id":"1d3eed5e","parentId":"056c28af","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:41:17.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0da1e0d0a8a9822b0169d4d13798288196ac81a462bf67a98b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，走 **方案 B**。  \n我下一步换工具链，不再硬顶 `r2` 大段输出，改成更适合做这类 so 的方式去抠：\n\n- `objdump -d`\n- `strings -t x`\n- `nm -D`\n- 必要时配合局部符号/字符串交叉定位\n\n目标不变，还是只盯这几条：\n\n- `PopRequest::getSign`\n- `BaseVodRequest::fillPopRequestInfo`\n- `onCacheUrlHashCallback`\n- `getApkSignHash1`\n- `decryptPlayAuth`\n\n我拿到第一批更硬的字段链后，再直接给你结论，不水。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0da1e0d0a8a9822b0169d4d137b9d8819687762e7a81e660aa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":46992,"output":168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775554865379,"responseId":"resp_0da1e0d0a8a9822b0169d4d135ff148196b412dc86f7e167c9"}}
