{"type":"message","id":"94ce5571","parentId":"6f63dfed","timestamp":"2026-04-07T13:06:55.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0531ed13b4ec2f130169d50169ffec8195b90e1a84da649986\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已记住。  \n以后这类题我会优先按这个工作流走：\n\n1. **先定主类**：web / reverse / pwn / forensics，不乱切  \n2. **先拿真实证据**：接口、响应、媒体直链、参数，不先脑补  \n3. **网页/API 能推进就先推进**，不要过早跳 reverse  \n4. **遇到 App/SDK 痕迹再补静态/动态**，当成增强链路  \n5. **先确认“能不能复现/能不能拿到资源”**，再追签名细节  \n6. **区分三层东西**：\n   - 网页可直接拿到的\n   - App 请求签名层\n   - 播放 URL 二次处理层\n7. **优先给阶段性结论**，不等“全还原”才汇报\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以把这套流程再沉淀成一版更短的“CTF 侦察工作流模板”。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0531ed13b4ec2f130169d5016a26cc81958799c79c99789532\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":47413,"output":244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775567206355,"responseId":"resp_0531ed13b4ec2f130169d5016827948195851179c36fdfc908"}}
