{"type":"message","id":"ae2f5e68","parentId":"27f2e2a1","timestamp":"2026-04-07T14:46:49.452Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/replay_auth_selftest---13943f25-55e3-4b4e-a35d-7c62dedc833d (application/octet-stream)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1775573208126-b2ab7055\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-07 22:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1775573209443}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e1dfedf","parentId":"ae2f5e68","timestamp":"2026-04-07T14:47:12.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0cc8a5918ca5b3850169d518e325ec81979eb093c7c6dd5e7b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我收到了一个附件，但它现在显示的是一个通用二进制文件：\n\n- `replay_auth_selftest---13943f25-55e3-4b4e-a35d-7c62dedc833d`\n- 类型：`application/octet-stream`\n\n我还不知道它具体是什么。  \n如果你要我继续处理，我可以直接帮你：\n\n1. **识别文件类型**\n2. **提取可读内容**\n3. **判断它和刚才 CTF / replay_auth / selftest 有什么关系**\n\n你只要回一句：\n\n- **“读这个附件”**\n\n我就直接开始。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0cc8a5918ca5b3850169d518e3448481978bb3a42f52b40aea\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":50346,"output":151,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775573209450,"responseId":"resp_0cc8a5918ca5b3850169d518e11844819784347046ddc72265"}}
